data.name: lblRulesList.Text
data.value: 1. Poison a cup 2. Choose: drink or tip? - if you drink, select a cup and you will drink it. If it is poisoned, you lose. - if you tip, select a cup and it will be tipped out. If it is poisoned, you win. You have 2 chances to tip out the right cup, if you don't tip the right cup in this time, you lose.
